_Information You Provide to Us Directly_

Adaya may collect Personal Information from you that to you voluntarily
provide to us in various ways, including but not limited to:

Creating an account;

Booking a Strategy Session;

Completing any online forms on the Site;

Purchasing our products or services from us;

Call, e-mail, or otherwise communicate with us and/or third parties contracted
by Adaya;

Respond to marketing e-mails; or

Otherwise interact with our Services or other Adaya platforms.
